--- !u!114 &175373621
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 175373619}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 48fdfcc8a67199e4aa51c8e7b7b14715, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WitcherRightVersion.Dialogue.DialogueInteractable
  displayName: Elder Voytsekh
  interactionPrompt: Talk
  startNodeId: start
  returnToElderNodeId: return
  completedQuestNodeId: completed
  dialogueNodes:
  - Id: start
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: 'Witcher. The whole road is open before you now: village, forest, swamp,
      ash tract. But the contract is still simple. Find what drags people into the
      reeds.'
    Choices:
    - Text: I accept the swamp contract.
      NextNodeId: accepted
      FlagToSet: acceptedSwampContract
      QuestAction: start_swamp_contract
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why is the village so eager to blame the swamp?
      NextNodeId: doubt
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: doubt
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Because fear needs a shape. Give it teeth, call it a beast, and people
      sleep. Start south if you want coin.
    Choices:
    - Text: I accept. But I will look deeper.
      NextNodeId: accepted
      FlagToSet: acceptedSwampContract
      QuestAction: start_swamp_contract
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Not yet.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: accepted
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Good. Speak with Marta, then follow the road into the Black Swamp. Bring
      proof before asking for reward.
    Choices:
    - Text: I am going.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: return
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: You came back from the reeds. Tell me the thing is dead.
    Choices:
    - Text: The drowner is dead. Here is your proof.
      NextNodeId: choice_response
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: returned_to_elder
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Not yet.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: choice_response
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Then the village can call this finished. The swamp gave us a beast, and
      you cut it down.
    Choices:
    - Text: The swamp is guilty. Pay me.
      NextNodeId: reward
      FlagToSet: MayorSupported
      QuestAction: accepted_elder_version
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: This is not just a monster. Something is wrong here.
      NextNodeId: warning
      FlagToSet: questionedElderVersion
      QuestAction: questioned_elder_version
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: warning
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Careful. A clean ending is a mercy in a place like this.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will take the reward. I am not done looking.
      NextNodeId: reward
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: reward
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: Take your coin, your experience, and Marta's antitoxin recipe. Spend them
      before questions spend you.
    Choices:
    - Text: Contract complete.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: swamp_contract_reward_received
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: completed
    SpeakerName: Elder Voytsekh
    Body: The road is quiet. The village prefers quiet.
    Choices:
    - Text: For now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
